{
  "stem": "10359.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And the-- one of the girls who was secretary to the general supervising that town, she was his lover, or girlfriend, whatever.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So they gave me a job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But they put me in a German uniform with a swastika on the arm.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And they gave me a rifle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And I had to supervise the, these-- the Soviet war prisoners, how they're cutting down the trees in the forests.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this was-- [LAUGHS] I told you it's like a time warp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know where I-- where I am.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But Dorothy was in a hospital at that time because they cut off her finger, as she was wounded.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she was, you know, on those false papers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I used to come into the hospital saying, heil, with a rifle and everything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I tried to put it on very, very believable so they wouldn't suspect it because I was very insecure.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I had to, to make it look or sound better than what actually it was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they shouldn't suspect anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because if you hide and you walk around like this, you're not sure of yourself, somebody will pick it up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I had to act very secure and very pompous.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's what happened with my two friends that helped me tremendously.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They are-- one of them is in Florida-- the whole family a a matter of fact.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He didn't tell them that I'm Jewish until about a year after the war because he was afraid somebody might say something.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they didn't know all the time while I was in that town, which called Slavuta, where Dorothy was in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They didn't know all the time that I was there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Did you look Jewish?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If I-- didn't-- no, I did not look Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had blonde hair?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had blonde hair, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Especially when you put the uniform even on the dark hair, you look-- he looks uniformly, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Do you know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So with a uniform, and rifle, and blond hair, I look like real.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But this wasn't the real army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was the engineering group called Todt organization.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Todt.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "T-O-D-- T-O-D-T, Todt.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They are-- that's the engineer-- engineering group, group from the-- from the army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But on Hitler's birthday or any other special thing, we had to go down the basement.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to drink beer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And sitting at the same table with the SS men who just came in from, from looking at people, for the underground people from the woods, with all the German soldiers sitting at the same table drinking beer with them.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had no idea I'm next to them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's very interesting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The only thing-- twice it happened that I was in a panic because once everybody had to go for a medical exam.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the second time I think was something similar.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that's the time I came to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I told Dorothy that something is-- I don't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "If I have to go for a medical exam or something, then I'm cooked.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So what happened is I slept in that-- what do you call-- Kaserne, in that place where all the other soldiers and SS-- everybody slept in that place.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a big [? camp. ?] So I got-- when she came out of the hospital, I took a room nearby.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I still worked for them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I took a room nearby.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was on crutches.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We lived in that room, not for too long.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somehow-- I don't remember now how I escaped, and how I got out of it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because if I-- if I would have gotten for the medical exam, then forget it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that's what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The same table.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Long table.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, all the SS men, and all the German army, and everybody.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nope.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was one that I suspected, but I don't think he was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even if he was, I mean he didn't let me know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I didn't let him know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was afraid even to talk to anybody.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I spoke Polish and German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "N-- I had a Polish German acc-- German accent, but not Jewish accent, not a Jewish accent.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- I was afraid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, it wasn't any-- you see, it's not easy, especially being-- hiding out like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But even hiding out after the second Aktion in Ostrog wasn't easy because you couldn't walk on the sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You had to walk in the middle of the street.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When you saw a Ukrainian or German soldier you have to take off your hat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You couldn't shake hands with a non-Jew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And was-- I told you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's was like a time warp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, you didn't know where you were.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
